{"tid":382121,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"得閒練字","createTime":"2017-08-31T12:58:54.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-01T03:55:44.000Z","uid":137918,"like":8,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"1d886c82389aa7bb3cce2e90d2a71687caf15664","tid":382121,"uid":137918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T12:58:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/31/205543_a42a8b59e607a050d0d3d921e1b28040.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F31%2F205543_a42a8b59e607a050d0d3d921e1b28040.jpg&h=af8bbb3b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n小弟手字絕對唔係靚，只係得閒無聊想練下寫字，你講低我就寫，不過只係寫繁體中文字啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同埋，大概兩句好了，太多真係搞唔掂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"624fbe48160b440547680ca46a101a93376ab0a8","tid":382121,"uid":50744,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T13:04:51.000Z","msg":"能不能請你安靜點"},{"pid":"ac124a3f2a052b25553acb03c73e43a41a5600ab","tid":382121,"uid":102968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T13:09:03.000Z","msg":"魑魅魍魉"},{"pid":"ec07f5a3f938e8e1127da044de544857b9958516","tid":382121,"uid":137918,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T13:09:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>能不能請你安靜點</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/31/210826_5b4de5a869cdeb2758c4efce4f5dfef3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F31%2F210826_5b4de5a869cdeb2758c4efce4f5dfef3.jpg&h=0984f814&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n會唔會係叫緊我安靜點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d9b2d9d81b7adaefc92b5fa5a1aff8852f95982","tid":382121,"uid":50744,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T13:11:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>能不能請你安靜點</blockquote><br />\n<img src=